OL,6,FFood and drink manufacturers have
OL,7,Freduced salt by a third, and sugar and
OL,8,Fcalories by a quarter in a typical
OL,9,Fshopping basket since 2015, according
OL,10,Fto a study.
OL,12,FMember firms of the Food and Drink
OL,13,FFederation (FDF) now contribute 33%
OL,14,Fless salt, 25% less sugar and 24%
OL,15,Ffewer calories to the British grocery
OL,16,Fmarket compared with 2015, according
OL,17,Fto the data from Kantar Worldpanel.
