OL,4,Cless salt than in 2015 ` Kantar
OL,6,FReformulation comes as the UK
OL,7,Fgradually introduces various pieces of
OL,8,Fnew legislation to target foods high
OL,9,Fin fat, salt and sugar (HFSS) as part
OL,10,Fof a broader effort to combat obesity
OL,11,Fand improve public health.
OL,13,FThese have included the 'sugar tax' `
OL,14,Fofficially called the Soft Drinks
OL,15,FIndustry Levy ` which added a charge
OL,16,Fof 24p on drinks containing 8g of
OL,17,Fsugar per 100ml and 18p a litre on
OL,18,Fthose with 5-8g of sugar per 100ml,
OL,19,Ffrom April 2018 as part of the
OL,20,Fstrategy to tackle childhood obesity.
