OL,3,CTypical shopping basket contains third
OL,4,Cless salt than in 2015 ` Kantar
OL,6,FOn Thursday, Labour confirmed it will
OL,7,Fintroduce legislation to ban companies
OL,8,Fadvertising products deemed high in
OL,9,Ffat, salt and sugar (HFSS) on TV
OL,10,Fbefore 9pm.
OL,12,FIt will also include a total ban on
OL,13,Fpaid-for online adverts for these
OL,14,Fproducts, in an effort to tackle
OL,15,Fchildhood obesity.
OL,17,FThe ban, which had first been put
OL,18,Fforward by Boris Johnson's
OL,19,FConservative government in 2021, will
OL,20,Fcome into force in October 2025.
